- **System-IDs**: User-IDs, Request-IDs, Session-IDs, Transaction-IDs
- **Performance-Metriken**: Response-Times, DB-Query-Times, API-Call-Duration
- **Technical Details**: HTTP-Status-Codes, Error-Codes, Service-Names
